  "instructions": [
    "Rinse quinoa under cold water and drain. Preheat oil in a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic to the skillet; cook for about 3 minutes until translucent.",
    "Stir in cumin, salt, and pepper. Mix well.",
    "Gradually add quinoa and stir continuously to coat with oil mixture. Cook for about 1 minute on each side.",
    "Fold in carrot and parsley leaves. Cook for another 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add cilantro, lemon juice, and avocado slices. Toss gently to combine all ingredients evenly. Let sit for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Serve immediately as a raw-friendly snack or light meal accompaniment."
